50|$|In 2016, the FBI {{announced}} {{it was trying to}} retrieve around $1 billion in funds associated with 1Malaysia Development Berhad, an investment fund owned by the government of Malaysia. This was the largest single action ever brought under the <b>Kleptocracy</b> Asset Recovery Initiative.|$|E
