50|$|While {{the use of}} {{offshore}} business entities is not illegal in the jurisdictions where they are registered, and often not illegal at all, reporters found that some Mossack Fonseca shell corporations {{seem to have been}} used for illegal purposes including fraud, <b>kleptocracy,</b> tax evasion and evading international sanctions.|$|E
